<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - MonieDiary</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        h1, h2 { color: #333; }
        p { margin: 10px 0; }
        ul { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy for MonieDiary</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> <%= effectiveDate %></p>
    
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to MonieDiary. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our services, including our WhatsApp bot and web application.</p>
    
    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Your WhatsApp ID, username, and email (if provided).</li>
        <li><strong>Transaction Data:</strong> Details of transactions you log, such as amounts, recipients, and descriptions.</li>
        <li><strong>Device & Usage Data:</strong> Information such as IP address, browser type, and interaction with our services.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Store and retrieve your logged transactions.</li>
        <li>Provide insights into your financial activity.</li>
        <li>Improve our services and user experience.</li>
        <li>Ensure security and prevent fraud.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>4. How We Store and Protect Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Your data is stored securely in a PostgreSQL database, with embeddings for search purposes.</li>
        <li>We use encryption and security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access.</li>
        <li>We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data as long as you have an active account. If you request account deletion, your data will be permanently erased from our servers.</p>
    
    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, modify, or delete your data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing.</li>
        <li>Contact us for any privacy-related concerns.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>MonieDiary may integrate with third-party services (e.g., WhatsApp Cloud API). We are not responsible for their privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them separately.</p>
    
    <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated through our platform.</p>
    
    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <%= contactEmail %>.</p>
</body>
</html>
